{"header":"<h1>Module <code><span>Domains.Domains_constraints_unionfind_builder</span></code></h1>","type":"documentation","uses_katex":true,"breadcrumbs":[{"name":"Index","href":"../../../index.html","kind":"leaf-page"},{"name":"codex","href":"../../index.html","kind":"page"},{"name":"Domains","href":"../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Domains_constraints_unionfind_builder","href":"#","kind":"module"}],"toc":[],"source_anchor":null,"preamble":"<p>These functors are placed above a union-find aware non-relational domain (i.e. <a href=\"../Domains_constraints_nonrelational/Make/index.html\"><code>Domains_constraints_nonrelational.Make</code></a>). They create union between terms when certain operations are performed (for instance <a href=\"../Constraint_domains_sig/module-type-Domain_S/Binary_Forward/index.html#val-biadd\"><code>Constraint_domains_sig.Domain_S.Binary_Forward.biadd</code></a>) with one constant argument.</p>","content":"<div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module anchored\" id=\"module-MakeAdditive\"><a href=\"#module-MakeAdditive\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <a href=\"MakeAdditive/index.html\">MakeAdditive</a></span><span>\u000A  (<a href=\"MakeAdditive/argument-1-C/index.html\">C</a> : \u000A    <a href=\"../Constraint_domains_sig/module-type-DOMAIN_WITH_UNION/index.html\">Constraint_domains_sig.DOMAIN_WITH_UNION</a>\u000A      <span class=\"keyword\">with</span> <span><span class=\"keyword\">type</span> <span>('a, 'b) <a href=\"../Constraint_domains_sig/module-type-DOMAIN_WITH_UNION/Constraints/Relation/index.html#type-t\">Constraints.Relation.t</a></span> =\u000A             <span><span>(<span class=\"type-var\">'a</span>, <span class=\"type-var\">'b</span>)</span> <a href=\"../../Constraints/Relations/Additive/index.html#type-t\">Constraints.Relations.Additive.t</a></span></span>) : \u000A  <a href=\"../Constraint_domains_sig/module-type-Domain_S/index.html\">Constraint_domains_sig.Domain_S</a>\u000A    <span class=\"keyword\">with</span> <span><span class=\"keyword\">type</span> <a href=\"../Constraint_domains_sig/module-type-Domain_S/index.html#type-t\">t</a> = <a href=\"MakeAdditive/argument-1-C/index.html#type-t\">C.t</a></span>\u000A     <span class=\"keyword\">and</span> <span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <a href=\"../Constraint_domains_sig/module-type-Domain_S/Constraints/index.html\">Constraints</a> = <a href=\"MakeAdditive/argument-1-C/Constraints/index.html\">C.Constraints</a></span>\u000A     <span class=\"keyword\">and</span> <span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <a href=\"../Constraint_domains_sig/module-type-Domain_S/Query/index.html\">Query</a> = <a href=\"MakeAdditive/argument-1-C/Query/index.html\">C.Query</a></span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Builder for the simple &quot;constant difference relation&quot; <code>y = x + c</code>. This relation is defined at <a href=\"../../Constraints/Relations/Additive/index.html\"><code>Constraints.Relations.Additive</code></a>.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module anchored\" id=\"module-MakeLinearTwoVarEquality\"><a href=\"#module-MakeLinearTwoVarEquality\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <a href=\"MakeLinearTwoVarEquality/index.html\">MakeLinearTwoVarEquality</a></span><span>\u000A  (<a href=\"MakeLinearTwoVarEquality/argument-1-C/index.html\">C</a> : \u000A    <a href=\"../Constraint_domains_sig/module-type-DOMAIN_WITH_UNION/index.html\">Constraint_domains_sig.DOMAIN_WITH_UNION</a>\u000A      <span class=\"keyword\">with</span> <span><span class=\"keyword\">type</span> <span>('a, 'b) <a href=\"../Constraint_domains_sig/module-type-DOMAIN_WITH_UNION/Constraints/Relation/index.html#type-t\">Constraints.Relation.t</a></span> =\u000A             <span><span>(<span class=\"type-var\">'a</span>, <span class=\"type-var\">'b</span>)</span> <a href=\"../../Constraints/Relations/LinearTwoVarEquality/index.html#type-t\">Constraints.Relations.LinearTwoVarEquality.t</a></span></span>) : \u000A  <a href=\"../Constraint_domains_sig/module-type-Domain_S/index.html\">Constraint_domains_sig.Domain_S</a>\u000A    <span class=\"keyword\">with</span> <span><span class=\"keyword\">type</span> <a href=\"../Constraint_domains_sig/module-type-Domain_S/index.html#type-t\">t</a> = <a href=\"MakeLinearTwoVarEquality/argument-1-C/index.html#type-t\">C.t</a></span>\u000A     <span class=\"keyword\">and</span> <span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <a href=\"../Constraint_domains_sig/module-type-Domain_S/Constraints/index.html\">Constraints</a> = <a href=\"MakeLinearTwoVarEquality/argument-1-C/Constraints/index.html\">C.Constraints</a></span>\u000A     <span class=\"keyword\">and</span> <span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <a href=\"../Constraint_domains_sig/module-type-Domain_S/Query/index.html\">Query</a> = <a href=\"MakeLinearTwoVarEquality/argument-1-C/Query/index.html\">C.Query</a></span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Builder for a linear two variable equality relation <code>f1*x + f2*y + 0</code>, also called TVPE. This relation is defined at <a href=\"../../Constraints/Relations/LinearTwoVarEquality/index.html\"><code>Constraints.Relations.LinearTwoVarEquality</code></a>.</p></div></div>"}